_:N4b4bec731898402695bb3c21d85090ed <http://schema.org/description> "The Ministry of Justice is a major government department, at the heart of the justice system. We work to protect and advance the principles of justice. Our vision is to deliver a world-class justice system that works for everyone in society. " .
